# .xsilignore — files excluded from the .xsil archive during `xsil publish`
# Syntax mirrors .gitignore: globs, leading / anchors to root, trailing / for
# directories only, ! un-ignores a previously ignored path.
# Built-in exclusions (always applied): .git  .xsilignore  .DS_Store  Thumbs.db

# ── Build artefacts ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Pre-compiled ELF binaries are intentionally excluded; the package ships
# source + build instructions and the CLI/sim compiles on demand.
sim/bin/

# ── Toolchain (external — installed separately) ───────────────────────────────
# The toolchain/ tree documents where to get the compiler; the binaries
# themselves are not bundled in the .xsil archive.
toolchain/bin/
toolchain/lib/
toolchain/include/

# ── Editor / IDE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── OS noise ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# (also caught by the built-in list, duplicated here for documentation)
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Temporary files ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.tmp
*.log
